    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in a few areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and the suspension is beginning to feel soft. Cosmetically, there are visible scuffs on the bumpers and the interior upholstery has some staining and wear on the driver's seat. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics and doesn't mind a bit of character.",
