      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$49,500 - Experience automotive excellence with this breathtaking vehicle in truly mint condition! It has been kept in showroom-quality shape, with every surface looking flawless and every component performing perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a car that feels and looks brand new in every single way\u2014a true collector's dream!",
