    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the suspension is starting to feel loose and it will likely need new brakes within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable option who doesn't mind doing a bit of cosmetic or mechanical refreshing.",
      "price": 18500.0,
